definition: appearance/portrait/picture/government minister/(physics) phase/(literary) to appraise (esp. by scrutinizing physical features)/to read sb's fortune (by physiognomy, palmistry etc)
each other/one another/mutually/fret on the neck of a pipa 琵琶[pi2 pa5] (a fret on the soundboard is called a 品[pin3])
as incompatible or irreconcilable as ice and hot coals

sentences.english: And you are saying wait a minute, he has violated the Pauli Exclusion Principle.
sentences.chinese: 你們有人在喊我停一下，說我違反了保利不相容原理。

sentences.english: Its optimal solution is obtained by finding a nonnegative solution of compatible equations.
sentences.chinese: 其最優解是通過求一個相容方程組的非負解而得到。

sentences.english: Religious viewpoints need not conflict with science.
sentences.chinese: 宗教信仰並非一定就與科學水火不相容。

sentences.english: The main objection to animalism is that it conflicts with the psychological-continuity view.
sentences.chinese: 對動物論的主要反對是，這和心理連續觀點不相容。

sentences.english: The results showed that the insecticides were more compatible with B. bassiana than the fungicides.
sentences.chinese: 結果表明，殺蟲劑與球孢白僵菌的相容性好於殺菌劑。

sentences.english: Conclusion CCHA has good biocompatibility and bone induction.
sentences.chinese: 結論CCHA具有良好的生物相容性和骨誘導作用。

sentences.english: Both molecules are incompatible with ferric salts.
sentences.chinese: 這兩種分子都與鐵鹽不相容。

sentences.english: The match is based on how compatible the tissues are and on the severity of the illness of the heart patient.
sentences.chinese: 根據組織相容性和患者病情的嚴重程度來決定配型。

sentences.english: The THOG problem is a paradigm to study the exclusive disjunction.
sentences.chinese: THOG問題是研究不相容選言推理的一個實驗範式。

sentences.english: In this paper, the compatibility of JUS organ polysiloxane gel was studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了JUS有機硅凝膠與各種材料的相容性問題。

sentences.english: This paper reports the result of biomaterial compatibility evaluation of hydrogel HFMC.
sentences.chinese: 本文報告了水凝膠HFMC的生物相容性評價結果。

sentences.english: The self-made cervical vertebral fusion cage has good biocompatibility.
sentences.chinese: 自制頸椎融合器有較好的生物相容性。

sentences.english: Is non-public ownership compatible with socialism? the traditional answer is negative.
sentences.chinese: 非公有制經濟同社會主義相容嗎？

sentences.english: How can God be sovereign and man still be free?
sentences.chinese: 神的主權和人的自由能相容嗎？

sentences.english: Some items affect the compatibility value between GF and party members.
sentences.chinese: 某些物品可以影響隊員與GF之間的相容性。

sentences.english: Human comprehensive development will advance new demands to the incentive compatibility constraint in Nanjiecun.
sentences.chinese: 人的全面發展對南街村激勵相容約束提出了新要求。
